ronment to motivate and challenge you? Group Exercise has it all, for every person and for every level. The Rec Center offers a variety of group ex formats to provide you with the oportunity to get great workouts led by experienced instructors. Classes are motivating, fun, and challenging for all fitness levels. Group Ex can help tone your major muscles, improve cardiovascular endurance, increase flexibility, and more. Participants must sign in upstairs, inside the group ex rooms. Classroom doors will be locked when class is scheduled to begin and no entrance will be permitted after the class has started. Classes are subject to change or cancellation due to low participation; classes must have a minimum of 2 participants. Participants must be 16 years of age.**PASSES WILL NOT BE REPLACED IF LOST OR STOLEN** GROUP EX CLASS SCHEDULES Download a copy of the Maymester 2017 GX schedule: Maymester 2017 GX Schedule Download a copy of the Spring 2017 GX schedule: Spring 2017 GX Schedule COMING SOON!  Download a copy of the Summer I 2017 GX schedule: Summer I 2017 GX Schedule GROUP EX PASSES Stop by the Rec Center's Member Services desk to purchase your Group Exercise pass.Spring 2017 GX passes are valid January 15 - May 13. Maymester 2017 GX passes are valid May 15 - June 3. Summer 2017 GX passes are valid June 4 - August 11. PASSES PRICING Spring Unlimited (HALF PRICED NOW!) $27.50 Summer Unlimited $45 20 classes $35 10 classes $25 Single class $3 GROUP EX SPECIALS May 7 - May 13 (Maymester) All classes free May 29 Reduced Group Ex Schedule July 4 Reduced Group Ex Schedule August 15 - August 26 Free and Reduced Group Ex Classes                             Visit Us  Pohl Recreation Center        1900 Chestnut Drive Denton, Texas 76203         Mail Us   1900 Chestnut Drive Denton, Texas 76203       Contact Us   940-565-2275 recsports@unt.edu Technical issues?                 Site last updated on May 05, 2017  Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State